            "items": [
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": "<p> </p>\n<p><br/>\n<br/>\nBeantwoord in de volgende eindexamenvragen:<br/>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"http://www.eindexamensite.nl/iframe-page.html?tx_iframequestion_pi1%5Bquestion%5D=11552&amp;template=1\" onclick=\"window.open(this.href, '', 'resizable=no,status=no,location=no,toolbar=no,menubar=no,fullscreen=no,scrollbars=no,dependent=no,width=750,height=550'); return false;\">Havo Biologie 2013-2 pilot vraag 2</a><br/>\nTwee afbeeldingen die in deze examenvraag staan, staan ook in Binas.<br/>\nZoek maar op! Die kun je dus altijd gebruiken.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.eindexamensite.nl/iframe-page.html?tx_iframequestion_pi1%5Bquestion%5D=1162&amp;template=1\" onclick=\"window.open(this.href, '', 'resizable=no,status=no,location=no,toolbar=no,menubar=no,fullscreen=no,scrollbars=no,dependent=no,width=750,height=300'); return false;\">Havo Biologie 2010-1 vraag 19</a><br/>\n<a href=\"http://www.eindexamensite.nl/iframe-page.html?tx_iframequestion_pi1%5Bquestion%5D=1164&amp;template=1\" onclick=\"window.open(this.href, '', 'resizable=no,status=no,location=no,toolbar=no,menubar=no,fullscreen=no,scrollbars=no,dependent=no,width=750,height=300'); return false;\">Havo Biologie 2010-1 vraag 21</a><br/>\n<a href=\"http://www.eindexamensite.nl/iframe-page.html?tx_iframequestion_pi1%5Bquestion%5D=1165&amp;template=1\" onclick=\"window.open(this.href, '', 'resizable=no,status=no,location=no,toolbar=no,menubar=no,fullscreen=no,scrollbars=no,dependent=no,width=750,height=300'); return false;\">Havo Biologie 2010-1 vraag 22</a><br/>\n<a href=\"http://www.eindexamensite.nl/iframe-page.html?tx_iframequestion_pi1%5Bquestion%5D=1166&amp;template=1\" onclick=\"window.open(this.href, '', 'resizable=no,status=no,location=no,toolbar=no,menubar=no,fullscreen=no,scrollbars=no,dependent=no,width=750,height=300'); return false;\">Havo Biologie 2010-1 vraag 23</a><br/>\n </p>\n"
